reviewText: This is a great movie that we love to take along on long car rides.  Keeps my son entertained and it has a cute storyline (Elmo tells Abby how great it is to go on car rides as she never rode in a car before.  They sing songs, talk about wearing seat belts, and even make potty stops along the way).
